Definition: the religious belief that between creature and creator no similarity can be found so great but that the dissimilarity is always greater
Example: any analogy between God and humans will always be inadequate
Synonyms: apophatism, cataphatism, analogy, religion, the, religious, belief, that, between, creature, and, creator, no, similarity, can, be, found, so, great, but, dissimilarity, is, always, greater, any, God, humans, will, inadequate
Category: noun.cognition
